::Battera::

She flaps her wings and stretches them out to full span.  Looks at how far 
her pod came close to hitting the Pred ship.

" Oh boy, that was only by a few yards.  Oh man, had I hit the ship at the 
speed of impact I'd be a goner.  Oh well, I'm a live and feeling fine."

She smiled to herself.  She wondered if anyone was home in the ship she 
nearly hit.
